<h1 class="title"><a href="#id1"><span class="problematic" id="id2">:mod:`reprlib`</span></a> --- Alternate <a href="#id3"><span class="problematic" id="id4">:func:`repr`</span></a> implementation</h1>

<div class="system-message" id="id1">
